{"tid":455823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「網上情緣」詐騙個案上升　警方籲勿輕信網上所謂朋友","createTime":"2017-11-02T12:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T12:33:45.000Z","uid":69197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aa374d7fb715399eda7120b0d07dfe2effe20dd1","tid":455823,"uid":69197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:25:45.000Z","msg":"警方搗破一個涉及香港及馬來西亞的跨境「網上情緣」詐騙集團， 兩地共拘捕11人，涉款約3千萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n警方網絡安全及科技罪案調查科總督察許綺惠表示，本港「網上情緣」詐騙個案有上升趨勢，警方今年首9個月共接獲142宗個案，較去年同期的72宗，上升97%； 今年首9個月的損失金額共7800多萬元，較去年同期上升37%。<br />\n<br />\n許綺惠又說，「網上情緣」的受害人超過9成是女性，主要是白領和專業人士，亦有家庭主婦，甚至退休人士，大部分騙徒會自稱來自歐美地區，聲稱是專業人士、跨國企業高層，甚至是軍人和船長等。<br />\n<br />\n許綺惠提醒市民，不要輕易相信在網上認識的所謂「朋友」，如果發現自己受騙，應盡快報警求助，曾經有個案是警方與相關銀行溝通後，成功截取匯款，替受害人取回部分損失金額。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1362717-20171102.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1362717-20171102.htm&d=cPaJDcXG9XQolH6S26n0sqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7d2bece1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1362717-20171102.htm&h=8db7ebe6\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1362717-20171102.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/202523_561cad12c12e078734e024f4c10e30a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F202523_561cad12c12e078734e024f4c10e30a7.jpg&h=e4cfdbf0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4296e9854ca99ab8c46d2a1c754c438f5d08a49","tid":455823,"uid":81183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:28:50.000Z","msg":"18-65歲 港女都愛洋腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e707680a5d91db87458c78e8d85308504103bbc","tid":455823,"uid":116688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:29:27.000Z","msg":"洋腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b44f35d1bd6afcf536f5e70aecf7c46b38e784a","tid":455823,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:33:45.000Z","msg":"超過九成是女性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}